staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100014: (안함)Oh! Well this is a little disappointing...
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100015: (안함)I had hoped he'd come and do it himself...
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100016: (안함)Oh! But maybe that was a bit rude of me.
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100017: (안함)I didn't mean to suggest I wasn't thankful!
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100018: (안함)Just disappointed. In the circumstances. Not in you.
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100019: (안함)I suppose I should give you some kind of reward?
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100020: (안함)Maybe that will be of some use to you?
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100025: (안함)^c:1486b0;Oscar^c:pop; really does keep this place tidy...
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100026: (안함)I wonder how he manages to find the time to clean an entire village of miscreants by himself?
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100028: (안함)Why, I certainly cannot tell you that! We fey value our privacy!
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100029: (안함)Do I miss being coated in rubbish?
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100030: (안함)Well... I did spend many a year that way...
staxel.village.dialogue.Alua.line:100031: (안함)But no, of course not! I had even begun to forget the scent of flowers!
